overview: The user wanted to elevate the aesthetic appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they felt was too generic. The assistant conducted a
  detailed review of the existing design, identifying areas like the color
  palette, backgrounds, form sections, and overall visual personality as needing
  improvement. The approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed
  color scheme, enhancing the main questionnaire form with decorative elements
  and a polished progress bar, and redesigning the Intro and Report sections for
  better visual engagement. Key UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons,
  and sliders were also updated to align with the new aesthetic. The outcome is
  a significantly more refined and professional-looking application that better
  reflects its purpose as a sleep health assessment tool.
